\" />"},{"pid":"2285b3fbed6c4336579ef04e80b45e6e6fe1a87d","tid":2382982,"uid":176002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43c11af11bffe256761af56af60e449b650ad6ef","tid":2382982,"uid":196666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"52975bfa213d578b27c7d61179c08d0831e1dc59","tid":2382982,"uid":204206,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣，日日返到屋企沖涼就忍唔住喊。覺得自己好垃圾，俾人話會一直都平伏唔到，一直低落。真係唔知點先可以改善自己抗壓能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T16:58:16.000Z","msg":"真係頂唔順而你身體比warning你嘅話就最好辭職唞下(前提自己要有d錢for你休息個陣用)<br />\n<br />\n利申：唞左一排就快返新工，但都驚到係咁諗新工會有好多嘢做好大壓力，不斷勁多負能量出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4300b9f624fbf1048c66768ed5b23fab1ff3b567","tid":2382982,"uid":342691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6318e5ff93e80dbc26c4687cd05931450d8911fe","tid":2382982,"uid":196666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd4432fd8c68a4f4d64abc768c23db07d05ec2e","tid":2382982,"uid":342691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:27:22.000Z","msg":"係咪第一份工？<br />\n如果真係頂唔到就唔好死頂啦<br />\n正常黎講頭三個月都係最辛苦 要不斷適應<br />\n如果都係克服唔到而又冇經濟壓力咪遞信走<br />\n第時做到有心理病就麻煩了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:09:36.000Z","msg":"其實未必關自己事<br />\n唔好下下都覺得係自己問題<br />\n返工姐 東家唔打咪打西家<br />\n有糧出 盡咗力 做好自己份內事就算<br />\n唔好諗太多<br />\n我都係上年fg 依家返緊份閪工 前排日撚日比人屌<br />\n雖然好唔開心 不過睇開啲就冇野了"},{"pid":"52d36ce78abd04cb6da7baf6f7dd070795f52bc7","tid":2382982,"uid":288401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:09:10.000Z","msg":"樓主<br />\n好明白你<br />\n我諗住做一世個行消失左咁滯<br />\n好迷茫又唔知可以做乜 好心急咁求其搵左份<br />\n待遇唔算刻薄 但自己真係唔鐘意 喊左兩晚 日日愁眉苦臉 收工都無哂熱情去過生活 都有諗過點解啲同事得我唔得 頂左一個月 最後都係Quit<br />\nQuit左當下都無offer 諗住過埋年先算 咁啱有朋友介紹返左新工 完全無之前日日好厭惡返工嘅感覺 雖然唔叫好開心好鐘意<br />\n但有時唔夾就係唔夾 唔係你嘅錯嚟 唔好死頂傷身又傷心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e87ff4e82a1a4c2d722c3fadd2dfc9629c862b","tid":2382982,"uid":39699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a2fc27763064e7b34e7fcfad75a36d7c6d2434","tid":2382982,"uid":196666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6e87ff4e82a1a4c2d722c3fadd2dfc9629c862b","tid":2382982,"uid":39699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d28a731bbfb1279a6f4df96e9467df2c33733cf","tid":2382982,"uid":39699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19a2fc27763064e7b34e7fcfad75a36d7c6d2434","tid":2382982,"uid":196666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6e87ff4e82a1a4c2d722c3fadd2dfc9629c862b","tid":2382982,"uid":39699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdf896ed021e8c72e664362dfeff3ff11595433","tid":2382982,"uid":196666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d36ce78abd04cb6da7baf6f7dd070795f52bc7","tid":2382982,"uid":288401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:09:10.000Z","msg":"樓主<br />\n好明白你<br />\n我諗住做一世個行消失左咁滯<br />\n好迷茫又唔知可以做乜 好心急咁求其搵左份<br />\n待遇唔算刻薄 但自己真係唔鐘意 喊左兩晚 日日愁眉苦